{"synckey":1640822555,"updated":[{"bookId":"41975832","bookmarkId":"41975832_5_1389-1491","chapterUid":5,"markText":"我把西方新自由主义经济学和它的理论基础新古典经济学称为“空想资本主义”，因为它们描写的市场近似于封建社会的小工场作坊，和工业化以后的铁路时代、核能时代风马牛不相及，和西方工业化、现代化的历史没有现实关系。","range":"1389-1491","createTime":1640822555,"type":1},{"bookId":"41975832","bookmarkId":"41975832_4_1615-1695","chapterUid":4,"markText":"铁路是第一次工业革命的象征，一开始就是社会的系统工程，没有全线协作，铁路根本无法运行。自由讨价还价只能是手工作坊时代的工作方式，于工业体系内的各环节是不适用的。","range":"1615-1695","createTime":1640822471,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"前言 学“火箭科学”，打金融攻坚战","chapterUid":5,"chapterIdx":5},{"title":"自序","chapterUid":4,"chapterIdx":4}],"book":{"bookId":"41975832","version":81137874,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/65/YueWen_41975832/s_YueWen_41975832.jpg","title":"眉山金融论剑","author":"陈平","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KWI#3-%6NE0L9axZNHS2X9","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#221b19"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#221b19"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#221b19"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#362f2d"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#362f2d"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#362f2d"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#4e4643"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#4e4643"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#4e4643"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#4e4643"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#675e5b"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#675e5b"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#675e5b"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#807875"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#807875"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#807875"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#9a928e"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#9a928e"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#9a928e"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#9a928e"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#b4aca8"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#b4aca8"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#b4aca8"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#cec7c3"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#cec7c3"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#cec7c3"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#e9e2de"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#e9e2de"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#9a928e"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#b4aca8"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3E8E5"},{"key":"5/100","hex":"#F3E8E5"},{"key":"6/100","hex":"#270500"}],"dominate_color":{"hex":"#504845","hsv":[18.61515079729186,